CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, reads: "Pioneer's Family-Mal R. Goode, one of Pittsburgh's most prominent pioneers now is joining the ABC news department as a staff member.  Here he's shown with his lovely family.  Left to right, front row: Ronald, Mal, Mrs. Goode and Rosalia.  Standing: Roberta, Richard, Russell and Robert."  (Daughter Roberta was inserted into published photo).
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Goode family including son Robert, daughter Roberta, Mary Lavelle Goode, Mal Goode, daughter Rosalia "Cookie", and sons Ronald, Russell, and Richard, posed for Mary and Mal Goode's wedding anniversary in their living room with painting of forest, and other women seated in chairs against wall in background
